{"tid":1852090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《入來一人一句多謝手足》勇武手足幫狗狗消毒","createTime":"2020-01-30T09:45:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T05:22:05.000Z","uid":191474,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c4c7749dc644dec368eda3371578a28533d8d95b","tid":1852090,"uid":191474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:45:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">booom！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n紅磡﹑旺角及葵涌三區9小時內，分別發生四宗警署及警車遭擲汽油彈案！今日（30日）凌晨，紅磡及旺角警署曾先後遭掟汽油彈，紅磡警署外牆及對開地面被薰黑；而葵涌警署昨晚亦被掟汽油彈，警方曾於社交媒體上表示，「嚴厲譴責暴徒喪心病狂的行為。」另外，昨晚深夜11時許，一輛警方衝鋒車駛至旺角彌敦道與奶路臣街交界時，突然遭投擲3個汽油彈，警方經初步調查，案件列作縱火。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n旺角警車被掟汽油彈　警列縱火案<br />\n<br />\n昨日(29日)深夜11時許，據報一輛警方衝鋒車，駛至旺角彌敦道與奶路臣街交界時，突然遭投擲3個汽油彈。其中1個汽油彈擊中衝鋒車車尾、其餘2個則跌落在地上。據悉事件中無人受傷。大批防暴警察事後趕至到現場戒備。警方表示，據報一輛沿彌敦道往深水埗方向行駛，駛至上址時被投擲汽油彈，警方經初步調查，案件列作縱火，交由旺角警區刑事調查隊第六隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/427787/%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6-9%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E5%9B%9B%E5%AE%97-%E4%B8%89%E9%96%93%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E5%8F%8A%E8%A1%9D%E9%8B%92%E8%BB%8A%E9%81%AD%E6%93%B2%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F427787%2F%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6-9%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25AE%2597-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%2596%2593%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%258F%258A%25E8%25A1%259D%25E9%258B%2592%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%2593%25B2%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=cc74d1f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/427787/%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6-9%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E5%9B%9B%E5%AE%97-%E4%B8%89%E9%96%93%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E5%8F%8A%E8%A1%9D%E9%8B%92%E8%BB%8A%E9%81%AD%E6%93%B2%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">boom boom！</span></span><br />\n天水圍天瑞邨天瑞商場優品360分店，凌晨被兩名黑衣人投擲懷疑汽油彈，事件中無人受傷，毋須疏散。<br />\n<br />\n警方凌晨1時39分接獲保安報案，指聽到聲響，之後發現兩名男子投擲懷疑兩枚汽油彈後逃去。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，消防將火救熄，初步調查發現店內有多處燒焦痕跡，有櫥窗玻璃被打破，相信起火原因有可疑。警員於現場檢走一支玻璃瓶及懷疑玻璃碎片作進一步檢驗。案件列作縱火，交由元朗警區重案組第一隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<a href=\"https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1190917/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%B4%E5%9C%8D%E5%A4%A9%E7%91%9E%E5%95%86%E5%A0%B4%E5%84%AA%E5%93%81360-%E9%81%AD%E5%85%A9%E9%BB%91%E8%A1%A3%E4%BA%BA%E6%93%B2%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1190917%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259C%258D%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%2591%259E%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%2584%25AA%25E5%2593%2581360-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%2585%25A9%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2593%25B2%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=37ca7403\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1190917%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259C%258D%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%2591%259E%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%2584%25AA%25E5%2593%2581360-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%2585%25A9%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2593%25B2%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588&h=aa28d846\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1190917/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%B4%E5%9C%8D%E5%A4%A9%E7%91%9E%E5%95%86%E5%A0%B4%E5%84%AA%E5%93%81360-%E9%81%AD%E5%85%A9%E9%BB%91%E8%A1%A3%E4%BA%BA%E6%93%B2%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">boom boom boom！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n三黑衣人葵涌警署外擲汽油彈　刑事調查隊跟進<br />\n<br />\n葵涌警署晚上懷疑遭汽油彈投擲，事件中無受傷。晚上8時12分，警署車閘外對出葵富路位置突然起火，警員在場調查，警方初步相信曾有3名蒙面人向警署投擲約3枚懷疑汽油彈。<br />\n<br />\n有傳媒公開網上影片稱是「讀者提供」片段，但拍攝位置卻明顯是警署位置。片段所見有 3 名身穿全身黑衣衫褲、白波鞋的男子，在葵芳邨方向步出，站在行人路上投擲四個汽油彈。<br />\n<br />\n警員事後在葵富路熏黑位置附近檢走卡式石油氣罐、玻璃碎等，警方將案件列作縱火案處理，交由葵青警區刑事調查隊第二隊調查。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%89%E9%BB%91%E8%A1%A3%E4%BA%BA%E8%91%B5%E6%B6%8C%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E5%A4%96%E6%93%B2%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E5%88%91%E4%BA%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E9%9A%8A%E8%B7%9F%E9%80%B2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2591%25B5%25E6%25B6%258C%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%25A4%2596%25E6%2593%25B2%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E5%2588%2591%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E9%259A%258A%25E8%25B7%259F%25E9%2580%25B2%2F&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=c9311b4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2591%25B5%25E6%25B6%258C%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%25A4%2596%25E6%2593%25B2%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E5%2588%2591%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E9%259A%258A%25E8%25B7%259F%25E9%2580%25B2%2F&h=b7f8137f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%89%E9%BB%91%E8%A1%A3%E4%BA%BA%E8%91%B5%E6%B6%8C%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E5%A4%96%E6%93%B2%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E5%88%91%E4%BA%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E9%9A%8A%E8%B7%9F%E9%80%B2/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">biu～</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方稱有人向天水圍警署擲汽油彈　暫時無人被捕<br />\n警方表示，有人向天水圍警署投擲汽油彈，暫時無人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n事發在清晨近5時，有人向警署投擲多枚汽油彈，無人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505378-20200129.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505378-20200129.htm&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=24e45780\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505378-20200129.htm&h=4d54ed6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505378-20200129.htm</a>"},{"pid":"60e3e969c1183a380da0f29121c80b142c6c2a84","tid":1852090,"uid":260100,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:47:08.000Z","msg":"啲BoomBoomBiu係咩事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5330f12fb3155befdd407123d02328ba5f8545c5","tid":1852090,"uid":191474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60e3e969c1183a380da0f29121c80b142c6c2a84","tid":1852090,"uid":260100,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:47:08.000Z","msg":"啲BoomBoomBiu係咩事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:47:38.000Z","msg":"...爆炸聲囉👉🏻👈🏻"},{"pid":"21c23108f93c29a65a0e78be320351a10602bbf4","tid":1852090,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60e3e969c1183a380da0f29121c80b142c6c2a84","tid":1852090,"uid":260100,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:47:08.000Z","msg":"啲BoomBoomBiu係咩事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:51:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw多謝勇武"},{"pid":"1ec5ba1eb4b1fe546a3079ae6f6400f5f08ef3bf","tid":1852090,"uid":297981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />萬事小心 <br />\n抗爭未完"},{"pid":"c178e28fa5f4ef1ecd8ea7153d85b20e24f97ee5","tid":1852090,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T10:13:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a378fdd825bc7913ecfdbd1ac1d90a8c3b3b458","tid":1852090,"uid":310474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T10:14:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b77bbe7cfc0273f71f768abb8a2fd132ecd24c1","tid":1852090,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T10:40:00.000Z","msg":"燒佢老母車"},{"pid":"856de2b2d35186293eff16a3e1028b1d09b1e097","tid":1852090,"uid":191474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T23:03:09.000Z","msg":"pishh"},{"pid":"e96903442dd397b8d890c0a880ed98b67cbdc2b6","tid":1852090,"uid":207247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T00:04:32.000Z","msg":"推，手足小心"},{"pid":"65d25ee2c7528c444ebc9ba087530fa98265bdd2","tid":1852090,"uid":47647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T00:05:35.000Z","msg":"多謝手足 請小心"},{"pid":"f5e56914d50102365727745c585aed7c2abdcd81","tid":1852090,"uid":24080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T00:20:19.000Z","msg":"多謝勇武手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a971637b28b555f92880a663eb6267fc3d346c","tid":1852090,"uid":166308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T00:30:06.000Z","msg":"多謝冇名英雄 請小心"},{"pid":"2f5f0a9543431dae6b6b303a95a57b8ca6dac52c","tid":1852090,"uid":38793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T00:38:12.000Z","msg":"Boom<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958d032b0595da95eb4d62e3a919ff1cca531dd0","tid":1852090,"uid":115769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T00:39:02.000Z","msg":"Much appreciatex"},{"pid":"8533ace52cd82a825b37b099e7356585e6468d84","tid":1852090,"uid":36155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T00:43:39.000Z","msg":"boom"},{"pid":"9bb87bd9d57d4a85d315e4c637f8b0ffc6918d7b","tid":1852090,"uid":151538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T00:47:11.000Z","msg":"核爆都唔割，最緊要小心行事、安全回家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4fb23061dff507ae5773719c26666c5a915cbe9","tid":1852090,"uid":279253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T00:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0009aa679e95e93c1d4bb907f902ef23928df2","tid":1852090,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T05:22:05.000Z","msg":"消毒要用酒精"}]}